--------------------------

DM_GLASSTOWER_NIGHT

--------------------------

Notes::

- This is the Night version of my 1st map DM_glasstower (http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/81845)

- The map has a few special additions:
* The 4 cars explode if you shoot the front... although one has an ofset hitbox for some reason, but still works.
* THERE IS NO HDR. i say this since i don't yet know how to add it... if you have HDR on things might look a little weird... just turn it off and the map is fine :)
* IS DESIGNED FOR DEATHMATCH. there are no buy zones or bomb zones or anything... yet.
* Each of the little houses has a "button" inside... shoot it and the glass explodes :D

- Map was designed for 24 PLAYERS.
